291 Emergency clause. In view of the emergency cited in the preamble, this legislation
302 takes effect when approved.
31 SUMMARY
3322 This bill establishes municipal cost components for state and county services provided
3333 to the unorganized territory that would normally be paid for by a municipality. The
3344 municipal cost components constitute the property tax for the unorganized territory.
